description:
The Pleiades are a team of special maids led by http://anidb.net/ch72781 [Sebas Tian], who were originally designed to protect and serve in the Throne room of http://anidb.net/ch95428 [Nazarick]. Despite each member, with the exception of Sebas, being weak by Nazarick`s standards, their strength is equivalent to a legendary monster in the New World.
Source: Wikipedia
name: Pleiades
